\sin(2x)=2\sin(x)\cos(x)
u=2x
 \int_0^\infty \frac{\sin^2(x)}{x^2}dx=-\lim\limits_{x\to \infty}\frac{\sin^2(x)}{x}+\lim\limits_{x\to 0}\frac{\sin^2(x)}{x}+\int_0^\infty \frac{2\sin(x)\cos(x)}{x}dx 
 \int_{0}^\infty \frac{\sin^2(x)}{x^2}dx=\int_0^\infty \frac{\sin(2x)}{x}dx 
 \int_{0}^\infty \frac{\sin^2(x)}{x^2}dx= \frac{\pi}{2} 
